data.title: The Other Change of Hobbit Science Fiction & Fantasy Bookstore: November 1996 Releases
data.text:
November 1996 Releases

Online ordering:

Select titles you'd like by checking off the boxes.

At bottom of this form, fill in your name and e-mail address.

(Important! We can't get back to you without this!)

Click on the Send Order button.

The order is transmitted to us. We will get back to you with availability and price.

Please be aware that some publishers may put a book out-of-print as early as three months after release. So it is possible that we may no longer have some of the following titles.

If your browser does not support forms, you can always send an order to us via e-mail: ochobbit@otherchangeofhobbit.com. Please read our page on further ordering policies.

We do try to answer our e-mail promptly. If you haven't heard back from us in a couple of days, please send us e-mail resubmitting the order.
